    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## Real or Not Real?\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze your fictional user's emails and evaluate your own phishing detection skills.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Upload your fictional user’s profile and emails to AI Chat.\r\n2. Tell the AI which messages you think are phishing, and explain why.\r\n3. Ask the AI if it agrees — and if it doesn’t, ask questions to understand what you missed.\r\n4. Share which human behaviors or emotions you think the phishing emails tried to exploit.\r\n5. Compare your ideas with the AI's response — were your instincts right? What were the “tells”?\r\n\r\n**Important:** Ask follow-up questions, explore different perspectives, or get clarification if you're unsure.\r\n\r\n\r\n**Try it out!**\r\n\r\n:::details [<i class=\"fa fa-briefcase\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i> **Need a starting prompt?**]\r\n>Here’s a fictional person’s profile and the messages they received. I think [X and Y] are phishing because [your reason]. Can you tell me if I’m right? \r\n\r\n>What human behaviors or emotions are being targeted in those messages?\r\n:::\r\n&nbsp\r\n\r\n\r\n",
    "submittable": "false",
